windy; Denver 32 cloudy; Des Moines 37 cloudy; Indianapolis 38
partly cloudy; Kansas City 41 partly cloudy; Minneapolis-St. Paul 36
foggy; Nashville 52 cloudy; New Orleans 54 foggy; St. Louis 49 fair.
